reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Exactly As Expected
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. This fit perfectly in my closet and elevates it completely. It took me a little over an hour to build it but I love this rack. I gave it 4 stars for two reasons: 1. One of the pieces cracked when I was pushing it into place, so not necessarily very durable but durable enough to do the job well (just don't put anything significantly heavy on it) 2. The wooden hammer they provided to put the rack together broke in the middle of the build. If the company is going to provide tools to build their items, they should not be flimsy.I would still most definitely recommend this rack. In fact after 3 people saw the results, I was asked to remodel their closets - ha!
